parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bag module can cause the air bags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.

the air bag module fails to deploy in a crash
the air bag module deploys unexpectedly
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

symptoms: The air bag warning light is illuminated
the air bag module fails to deploy in a crash
the air bag module deploys unexpectedly
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
